{"title":"vue-router参数传递","uid":"7eb05e44a1a24a1f35ae6986ac703c03","slug":"vue-router参数传递","date":"2021-04-28T02:24:31.000Z","updated":"2021-04-29T02:45:42.478Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vue-router参数传递.json","keywords":"html,css,javascript,vue,webpack,react,学习,分享","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"vue-router参数传递\"><a href=\"#vue-router参数传递\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vue-router参数传递\"></a>vue-router参数传递</h1><h2 id=\"通过-to-和-query-进行参数传递\"><a href=\"#通过-to-和-query-进行参数传递\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过 :to 和 query 进行参数传递\"></a>通过 :to 和 query 进行参数传递</h2><p><strong>URL</strong> 是表示资源位置的字符串。</p>\n<p><strong>解析URL</strong> (维基百科) <code>&lt;scheme&gt;</code> 方案+<code>&lt;host&gt;</code> 主机+<code>&lt;port&gt;</code> 端口+<code>&lt;hostport&gt;</code> 主机及端口+<code>&lt;path&gt;</code> 路径+<code>&lt;query&gt;</code> 请求+<code>&lt;fragment&gt;</code> 片段+<code>&lt;host-specific&gt;</code> 主机待定</p>\n<p>其中，query为请求</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>参考代码：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在入口vue文件App.vue中配置对应Profile文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- vue2 App.vue --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 注意：此处to加了:即v-bind:之后属性值才会是对象，否则就是普通的字符串 --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>router-link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">:to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>&#123;path:<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>/profile<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>,query:&#123;name:<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>zzwi<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>,gender:<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>man<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>&#125;&#125;<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Profile<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>router-link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- vue2 Profile.vue --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>我是Profile标题<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>我是Profile内容<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>&#123;&#123;$route.query.name&#125;&#125;<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>&#123;&#123;$route.query.gendle&#125;&#125;<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>运行效果</p>\n<h2 id=\"我是Profile标题\"><a href=\"#我是Profile标题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我是Profile标题\"></a>我是Profile标题</h2><p>我是Profile内容</p>\n<p>zzwi</p>\n<p>man</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"通过-methods-和-query-进行参数传递\"><a href=\"#通过-methods-和-query-进行参数传递\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过 methods 和 query 进行参数传递\"></a>通过 methods 和 query 进行参数传递</h2><p>在入口vue文件App.vue中设置methods</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// vue2</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// App.vue</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button @click<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"profileClick\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Profile<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>template<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'App'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    methods<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">profileClick</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>$router<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n          path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/profile'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          query<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'zzwi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            gendle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'man'</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"通过-params-进行参数传递\"><a href=\"#通过-params-进行参数传递\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过  params 进行参数传递\"></a>通过  params 进行参数传递</h2><p>通过配置路由格式</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 配置动态路由</span>\n    path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'/user/:id'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>在入口文件App.vue的路径传递方式:在path后面跟上对应的值</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>router-link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/user/123<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>router-link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>    \n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>之后便能生成路径：/user/123</p>\n","feature":null,"text":"vue-router参数传递通过 :to 和 query 进行参数传递URL 是表示资源位置的字符串。 解析URL (维基百科) &lt;scheme&gt; 方案+&lt;host&gt; 主机+&lt;port&gt; 端口+&lt;hostport&gt; 主机及端口+&l...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":11,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":11,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vue-router%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vue-router参数传递</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-to-%E5%92%8C-query-%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通过 :to 和 query 进行参数传递</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFProfile%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">我是Profile标题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-methods-%E5%92%8C-query-%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通过 methods 和 query 进行参数传递</span></a></li